remarks.format: ## Remarks 类包含标识隐式资源键的字段。The class contains fields that identify an implicit resource key. 隐式资源是按以下形式分配给控件的：An implicit resource is assigned to a control in the following form: ``` ``` 在页的分析过程中，隐式资源将以 [*filter*：]*前缀*形式转换为显式键。*属性*[。*子属性*]。During page parsing, an implicit resource is converted into explicit keys in the form [*filter*:]*prefix*.*property*[.*subproperty*]. 在前面的示例中) ，具有指定前缀 (的任何资源值 `Welcome` 都将分配给匹配的控件属性。Any resource values with the specified prefix (in the preceding example, a prefix of `Welcome`) are assigned to the matching control properties. 例如，假设值存在于以下键的资源文件或源代码中：For example, suppose values exist in the resource file or source code for the following keys: `Welcome.Text` `Ie:Welcome.Text` `Welcome.Forecolor` 这些值将分配给各自的控件属性。These values are assigned to their respective control properties. 隐式资源键只能引用本地资源。Implicit resource keys can reference only local resources.
